WEBVTT

00:11.209 --> 00:13.210
You Reagan?

00:13.212 --> 00:15.079
Yeah.
Eddie Janko.

00:15.081 --> 00:18.549
Sarge says we're, uh...
we're riding together.

00:20.151 --> 00:21.418
Something wrong?

00:21.420 --> 00:23.354
No, um, I was expecting a...

00:23.356 --> 00:25.055
Fat, sweaty Hungarian guy?

00:25.057 --> 00:26.090
(laughs)

00:26.092 --> 00:27.324
Sorry to burst your bubble.

00:27.326 --> 00:28.993
Uh, no offense.

00:28.995 --> 00:32.262
Oh, no, trust me,
it's really hard to offend me.

00:32.265 --> 00:34.265
My real name's Edit,
after my grandmother,

00:34.267 --> 00:37.401
but Eddie's just
easier all around.

00:37.403 --> 00:40.437
Okay, um, who was
your last partner?

00:40.439 --> 00:43.974
Actually, I just graduated
from the academy last week.

00:46.511 --> 00:48.045
Oh, seriously.

00:48.047 --> 00:49.413
You're my first, Reagan.

00:49.415 --> 00:50.648
Be gentle.

00:50.650 --> 00:52.349
I just meant,
all of my other partners

00:52.351 --> 00:54.671
have had at least as much time
on the job as me.

00:54.672 --> 00:56.155
Oh.

00:56.157 --> 00:58.157
Should I come back
in a few years?

00:58.159 --> 01:00.043
I'll let you know
after our tour.

01:00.045 --> 01:02.428
DISPATCH (over radio): All
units, 10-13 from the officer.

01:02.430 --> 01:03.880
Shots fired, corner of

01:03.882 --> 01:06.132
three-two and nine.
Units responding.

01:06.134 --> 01:08.284
That's us. So much
for starting slow. Hey!

01:08.286 --> 01:09.502
Do you mind if I drive?

01:09.504 --> 01:10.887
I don't think...
(engine starts)

01:12.139 --> 01:13.773
(siren wails)

01:13.775 --> 01:15.625
(tires squealing)
Hey, hey, whoa!

01:15.627 --> 01:17.160
(Jamie shouting indistinctly)

01:23.017 --> 01:25.818
(siren wails, then stops
as tires screech)

01:26.603 --> 01:28.087
Hey, what have you got?

01:28.089 --> 01:29.789
Responding
to a 10-30 in progress.

01:29.791 --> 01:31.824
That jewelry store, two perps.

01:31.826 --> 01:33.309
We took shots
when we came through the door.

01:33.311 --> 01:34.627
One of them flew out the back.

01:34.629 --> 01:35.712
I chased him, he got away.

01:35.714 --> 01:37.029
My partner went after
the other guy.

01:37.031 --> 01:38.665
(gunfire)

01:40.000 --> 01:46.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:48.976 --> 01:50.426
(woman groaning)

01:50.428 --> 01:51.678
We got a body.

01:51.680 --> 01:54.597
Hey... hey...

01:54.599 --> 01:55.848
(moaning)

01:55.850 --> 01:57.684
Collins...

01:57.686 --> 01:58.851
(gasping)

01:58.853 --> 02:01.404
Where are you hit?
(crying)

02:01.406 --> 02:03.156
Put pressure on it!
Put pressure on it!

02:03.158 --> 02:05.291
Lori, Lori,
where'd he go?

02:05.293 --> 02:07.226
(gasping):
He took off... through the park.

02:07.228 --> 02:09.946
Hang in there, Collins.
You're gonna be all right.

02:09.948 --> 02:11.164
JANKO: We have an officer shot.
Location: inside Lenox Avenue.

02:11.166 --> 02:13.282
Stay here.
Stay with her.

02:13.284 --> 02:15.067
Come on, come on!
Get her in!

02:17.371 --> 02:20.089
(Collins gasping rapidly)

02:23.877 --> 02:26.879
(Collins gasping)

02:26.881 --> 02:28.798
DISPATCH (over radio):
All units, 10-13.

02:28.800 --> 02:32.268
We have a confirmed officer shot
in Lenox Avenue park,

02:32.270 --> 02:34.086
vicinity of park house.

02:34.088 --> 02:35.855
Units respond.

02:35.857 --> 02:38.024
(sirens wailing)

02:44.198 --> 02:47.066
Officers Reagan and Janko
were first to respond.

02:47.068 --> 02:50.269
Officer Collins
is in surgery now.

02:50.271 --> 02:52.038
How bad?

02:52.040 --> 02:54.273
Took one to the
stomach under her vest.

02:54.275 --> 02:55.575
Lost a lot of blood.

02:55.577 --> 02:56.893
Commissioner.

02:56.895 --> 02:58.544
How's my officer?

02:58.546 --> 03:01.781
We did everything we could,
but there was too much damage.

03:01.783 --> 03:03.616
She died a few minutes ago.

03:03.618 --> 03:06.686
I'm sorry, Frank.

03:10.307 --> 03:12.558
Her husband's
in the chapel.

03:14.144 --> 03:15.511
I'll talk to him.

03:15.513 --> 03:17.597
With their
five-year-old daughter.

03:17.599 --> 03:20.466
Andrew and Katie.

03:23.103 --> 03:25.271
(sighs)

03:36.500 --> 03:38.701
We lost her.

03:44.157 --> 03:46.175
Sir, this is my partner.

03:46.177 --> 03:48.711
Officer Janko, sir.

03:48.713 --> 03:50.847
You going back to the scene?

03:50.849 --> 03:53.299
As soon as we talk
to the detectives.

03:53.301 --> 03:55.468
(sighs)

03:57.221 --> 03:59.839
We need to get
this son of a bitch.

04:02.726 --> 04:05.795
(sighs)

04:07.601 --> 04:11.601
<font color=#00FF00>♪ Blue Bloods 4x01 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Unwritten Rules</font>
